TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: One of our allies has built resource production on the side of a wide river delta. They are well defended from the north but unprotected from core attacks across the river delta. Your mission is to build a flagship and use its long range guns to destory the core control tower in the north east, but you must also patrol the waterways constantly and protect our ally's control towers. In return, our ally will share resources.

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: Intelligence indicates the enemy control tower is here.
